{"type":"message","id":"18d393f8","parentId":"46a5de9b","timestamp":"2026-05-14T07:36:57.640Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_o5qa8xpbmbp0_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[mcporter] Auto-corrected server name to sorftime-mcp (input: sorftime).\nsorftime-mcp\n\n  /**\n   * 授权失败\n   */\n  function NotAuthorization();\n\n  Examples:\n    mcporter call sorftime-mcp.NotAuthorization()\n\n  1 tool · 1775ms · HTTP https://mcp.sorftime.com/?key=zwpmsm…zz09"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2427,"aggregated":"[mcporter] Auto-corrected server name to sorftime-mcp (input: sorftime).\nsorftime-mcp\n\n  /**\n   * 授权失败\n   */\n  function NotAuthorization();\n\n  Examples:\n    mcporter call sorftime-mcp.NotAuthorization()\n\n  1 tool · 1775ms · HTTP https://mcp.sorftime.com/?key=zwpmsmvutwvimcs2mmlzu2vyl3dkzz09","cwd":"/home/halei/workspace-tts"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778744217639}}
{"type":"message","id":"3eb589e5","parentId":"18d393f8","timestamp":"2026-05-14T07:37:13.594Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is right - the key `zwpmsmvutwvimcs2mmlzu2vyl3dkzz09` that was working before seems to have expired or been revoked. The Sorftime MCP server now only returns `NotAuthorization()` - one tool, and it's not the actual data tools we were using.\n\nThis confirms what we suspected earlier - the key needs to be renewed. The user said \"充值就可以用了\" (just need to top up/recharge and it will work).\n\nSo the situation is:\n1. ✅ Sorftime MCP server is still running/accessible\n2. ❌ But the API key has expired/been revoked - only returns NotAuthorization\n\n\n3. The data tools we need like category searches, product searches, and influencer analysis aren't available until the account is recharged. I should let the user know the status clearly and ask if they want to proceed with the Coze workflow approach instead.","thinkingSignature":"c8373ff9944b997c947bb6ae1fa1e0e56ff4d9eead8c913a5a3926d8b507d0fe"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n你说得对，刚才测了一下——\n\n**Sorftime MCP 返回：`NotAuthorization()`**\n\nKey 过期了，现在只能测授权，不能调真正的数据接口。你说得对，充值就能恢复。\n\n---\n\n**现在有两条路：**\n\n**路线 A：等你充值 Sorftime**\n充值后 Key 恢复，我们继续按之前的方式跑——数据 + 写入飞书表格，图片问题走你说的 ID 替换方案\n\n**路线 B：先推进 Coze 工作流**\n你说的 Sorftime 官方搭的 Coze 工作流能读到图片——如果这条路能跑通，我们可以绕过 Sorftime，用 Coze 工作流作为图片获取层\n\n---\n\n你倾向哪条？如果 Coze 那条路能拿到接口或者 workflow 配置，我们现在就往那个方向推，不等充值。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":150,"output":349,"cacheRead":30784,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31283,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778744217656,"responseId":"0654ae995c65c1deec453ecb3d1b276c"}}
