{"type":"message","id":"eec2c603","parentId":"7f1b23ab","timestamp":"2026-05-14T07:37:23.639Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if the key has expired again. I just tested and confirmed it returned NotAuthorization(). The user is likely checking if my diagnosis is correct. Let me be direct - yes, the key has expired/not authorized.","thinkingSignature":"fe3f18337769d52f7a582f8ac16b8ceca985dc49d91570b9cf0d696d9f39ec31"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n对，确认是 Key 过期了——调用 Sorftime MCP 返回 `NotAuthorization()`，连不上数据接口。\n\n充值后就能恢复。你那边打算什么时候充值？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":9348,"output":82,"cacheRead":23200,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32630,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778744239138,"responseId":"0654aeaf7b8f15c9ece3cde917d1f9a0"}}
