{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6f63b44740b8c27c256ad5f79b1\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-05-14 15:54 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"ef61a652","parentId":"2e1ad116","timestamp":"2026-05-14T07:54:23.706Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"1076b355","parentId":"ef61a652","timestamp":"2026-05-14T07:55:12.386Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to explain my product selection logic - what would I do with the data once we have it (ProductId, title, price, sales volume, etc.) to select products.\n\nThis is a great question. Let me think about the SOP we discussed earlier:\n\nFrom the memory, we had a three-track selection strategy:\n1. 主动选品 - Active product hunting (using TikTok Shop backend / EchoTik data)\n2. 跟品策略 - Follow products (from hot lists, comparing with 1688)\n3. 1688直选 - Direct selection from 1688\n\nAnd the key filters from the SOP:\n- Low base, high growth trend products\n- New influencers in last 7 days > 10, new videos > 20\n- Total sales < 500, comment count < 100\n- Price range $5-$22 (or for Vietnam, ≥50,000 VND)\n- Output: Top 10 potential products\n\nFor flow:\n1. Category search → Category report (Top50 products)\n2. Filter: Monthly sales, price range, growth rate, comment count\n3. For promising products: influencer analysis (tail influencers < 100k fans driving > 60%)\n4. 1688 sourcing matching\n\nThe user is essentially asking: if we have all this data flowing in, what's my thought process for picking products from it?\n\nLet me explain the selection logic I would use:\n\n**Step 1: Classify products by stage**\n- New products (recently launched, low base, rapid growth) → 潜力品\n- Growing products (established, growing steadily) → 成长品\n- Mature products (high sales, stable) → 成熟品\n\n**Step 2: Key filters**\n1. Price: Must be in profit margin range\n   - Vietnam: ≥50,000 VND\n   - Thailand: corresponding range\n2. Sales momentum: Looking for products where weekly > monthly average, indicating upward trajectory rather than flat performance\n3. Competition level: Assessing how many similar products exist and their sales concentrations to determine if the market is oversaturated or has room for new entrants\n4. Rating/Review: Filtering for products with 4.0+ stars and manageable review counts\n5. Growth signals: Identifying products gaining traction through increasing sales velocity and new influencer partnerships\n\n**Step 3: Scoring**\nBased on the 170-point scoring system mentioned in the memory:\n- Growth rate (weekly/monthly ratio)\n- Sales rank in category\n- Profit margin potential\n- Competition index\n- New video/influencer activity\n\n**Step 4: 1688 matching**\nFor products that pass the filters, search 1688 for:\n- Same or similar products\n- Price comparison\n- Supplier reliability\n\nI'm also considering how the user mentioned Sorftime's Coze workflow that can pull images - this might be relevant to the selection process.\n","thinkingSignature":"c774be6aefff874466ecfc110e0f8240e551ba8c5007dd11c84393f4eb5e6182"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n这个问题问得好。假设数据现在都跑通了——类目报告、相似产品、产品详情、达人分析——我来描述一下我的选品逻辑：\n\n---\n\n## 第一步：过滤（筛掉明显不行的）\n\n| 维度 | 标准 | 原因 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **价格** | VN ≥50,000 VND / TH 对应区间 | 低于这个没利润 |\n| **月销量** | 100~500 | 太低没市场，太高竞争红 |\n| **评论数** | <200 | 评论少 = 产品新 or 销量小，机会更大 |\n| **评分** | ≥4.0 | 低于4.0质量问题多，退货率高 |\n| **上架时间** | 3个月内新品优先 | 新品竞争小，有爆相 |\n\n---\n\n## 第二步：找\"低基数高增速\"品\n\n核心公式：\n```\n周环比增长 > 30%  → 爆发迹象\n新增带货视频数 > 10（近7天） → 有达人开始推\n新增带货达人数 > 5（近7天） → 流量正在扩大\n累计销量 < 500 → 基數低，爆单空间大\n```\n\n举例：\n- A 品：月销 300，周环比 +60%，新增视频 15 个 → ✅ 进候选\n- B 品：月销 5000，周环比 +5%，新增视频 2 个 → ❌ 太卷了\n\n---\n\n## 第三步：验证流量质量（达人结构）\n\n调 `tiktok_product_video_author` 查带货达人分布：\n- **尾部达人（<10万粉）带货占比 > 60%** → 说明民间自发在推，不是纯品牌砸钱 → ✅\n- **头部达人（>100万粉）占比 ≥ 50%** → 说明靠大V硬推，小卖家跟不起 → ❌\n\n---\n\n## 第四步：1688 供应链匹配\n\n对通过前三步的产品：\n1. 从标题提取核心关键词\n2. 调 1688 搜索 → 找同款/相似品\n3. 筛选：起订量 ≤ 2、评分 ≥ 4.5、回头率 ≥ 15%\n4. 计算利润空间：`(TK售价 - 1688拿货价 - 运费 - 平台费) / TK售价`\n\n利润 < 20% 的直接淘汰。\n\n---\n\n## 最终输出\n\n给每个品打分（0-100），输出：\n- 商品名称 + TK链接\n- 价格 / 月销 / 增长率\n- 利润率 + 预估利润\n- IP风险\n- 行动建议：**跟 / 观望 / 1688询价**\n\n---\n\n**所以现在的问题回到原点：**\nSorftime Key 充值回来 + 图片问题解决 → 这套流程就能跑起来。\n\n你那边充值大概什么计划？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":799,"output":1190,"cacheRead":37408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39397,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778745263727,"responseId":"0654b2b09cbc2d9581b15a1ca13aded3"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0f23ddc2","parentId":"1076b355","timestamp":"2026-05-14T07:56:07.970Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[message_id: om_x100b6f6c4ff88090b102fb16db272f1]\nou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68: 1.ali1688_similar_product\n功能描述：通过 1688 平台查找产品的采购货源，可用于分析产品的采购成本价。跨境电商卖家可通过此接口对比 Amazon/TikTok/Walmart 平台上同类产品在 1688 的批发价格，评估利润空间。\n调用消耗：1\nsearchName\nString\n必填\n查询的产品名称（支持中英文）\npage\nInteger\n可选\n查询结果的页码索引，默认为第1页。每页返回50条数据。\n返回示例\n返回数据为便于 AI 大模型理解、并便于其引导使用数据的字符串，其中会携带相关数据。以下展示的数据结构为示意，但并非严格的 JSON 格式\n```\n[\n {\n \"标题\": \"空气炸锅批发多功能大容量电炸锅无油烟薯条机批汇演礼品厂家\",\n \"主图\": \"https://cbu01.alicdn.com/img/ibank/O1CN01eOpNFQ2K33kk3enb2_!!2208772849500-0-cib.jpg\",\n \"URL\": \"https://detail.1688.com/offer/778421220965.html\",\n \"价格\": 2.60,\n \"卖家\": \"深圳市云智牛科技有限公司\"\n }\n]\n\n```\n典型用途\n- **采购成本分析**： 输入 Amazon 上的热销产品名称，查询 1688 对应供货商的批发价，计算利润空间。\n- **供应商筛**： 通过返回结果中的卖家信息，筛选和对比不同供应商的报价。同一产品不同供应商价格差异可能很大。\n- **选品验证**： 结合 Amazon/TikTok 的销售数据，确认某产品在 1688 是否有充足的供应链支持。\n- **竞品价格监控**： 定期查询同类产品的 1688 价格变化，跟踪供应链成本波动。\n\n\n这是mcp返回的1688能力。有用吗，"}],"timestamp":1778745367965}}
{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6f6c4ff88090b102fb16db272f1\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-05-14 15:56 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"71c5f965","parentId":"0f23ddc2","timestamp":"2026-05-14T07:56:07.971Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"bb3339d0","parentId":"71c5f965","timestamp":"2026-05-14T07:56:37.481Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is sharing the 1688 MCP capabilities from Sorftime. Looking at this - `ali1688_similar_product` does return product data including an image URL (`主图`)! This is very useful because:\n\n1. We can use TikTok product titles → search 1688 → get 1688 product data with images\n2. The image URL from 1688 can serve as the product image in our Feishu table\n3. We can match TikTok products with 1688 suppliers for sourcing\n\nSo the workflow could be:\n1. Get TikTok products via Sorftime MCP (ProductId, title, price, sales)\n\n\n2. Use those TikTok titles to search 1688 via `ali1688_similar_product` and pull the main image along with supplier info and pricing\n3. Push everything to Feishu - the 1688 image becomes our product image while the TikTok data remains the core sales information\n\nThis is the missing piece we needed. The 1688 image fills the gap where TikTok product details don't include images.\n\nFor the selection logic itself, I'd filter TikTok products by sales volume to identify winners, verify 1688 availability to confirm sourcing is viable, and calculate profit margins by comparing the TikTok selling price against 1688 costs. The workflow runs through category reports for top performers, enriches each with 1688 image and supplier data, then scores everything before outputting to Feishu.","thinkingSignature":"e232ad95c2a41e2837f67d6555d4295532d3f22a1cda0e0e7491b4e290e31454"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**有用，而且很关键！** \n\n`ali1688_similar_product` **直接返回图片 URL**——`主图` 字段，这个就是我们一直在找的东西。\n\n---\n\n## 选品流程可以这样跑\n\n```\n1. TikTok 类目报告 → 拿到 Top50 产品（标题/价格/销量）\n      ↓\n2. 对每个品调 ali1688_similar_product → 拿到 1688 图片 + 货源 + 价格\n      ↓\n3. 写进飞书表格 → 产品图片用 1688 的，销量数据用 TikTok 的\n```\n\n**表格里的图片问题解决了**——不用抓 TikTok 的图，用 1688 的主图替代。\n\n---\n\n## 选品逻辑大概这样\n\n| 步骤 | 筛选条件 | 目的 |\n|------|----------|------|\n| 1. TikTok 价格 | ≥50,000 VND / $5+ | 保证利润空间 |\n| 2. 月销量 | 100-500（低基数高增速） | 蓝海品 |\n| 3. 评论数 | <100 | 竞争不充分 |\n| 4. 1688 有货 | 有货源且价格合理 | 供应链确认 |\n| 5. 1688 价 vs 售价 | 利润 ≥30% | 值得做 |\n\n---\n\n**现在 Key 充值回来就能跑。** 你那边决定充值了吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":13219,"output":594,"cacheRead":23200,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37013,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778745368020,"responseId":"0654b318a95367e7e52dc3882b420f42"}}
{"type":"message","id":"42745a78","parentId":"bb3339d0","timestamp":"2026-05-14T08:01:36.655Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[message_id: om_x100b6f6c5b72e48cc395e8038207674]\nou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68: 如果 sorftime 支持CLI 了 是不是就无敌了。"}],"timestamp":1778745696654}}
{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6f6c5b72e48cc395e8038207674\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-05-14 16:01 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"25d8a430","parentId":"42745a78","timestamp":"2026-05-14T08:01:36.656Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"ee48369b","parentId":"25d8a430","timestamp":"2026-05-14T08:02:14.480Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is sharing two things:\n\n1. The `ali1688_similar_product` tool from Sorftime MCP - this returns product title, **image URL** (主图), 1688 URL, price, and seller info. This is actually really useful! And importantly, it includes the image URL!\n\n2. A question about whether Sorftime CLI would make them \"unstoppable\"\n\nFor the first point - this is great! The `ali1688_similar_product` returns the product image URL! So even if Sorftime doesn't return Tiktok product images, we can get the 1688 supplier image as a fallback/proxy. Actually wait - the user wants to display product images in the Feishu table. The 1688 image is the supplier's product image, not the TikTok product image, but it at least gives a visual reference.\n\nFor the second point about Sorftime CLI - yes, if Sorftime supports CLI, it would make things much more stable and easier to integrate with OpenClaw. But let me focus on what's actionable now.\n\nActually, thinking about this more carefully:\n- Tiktok product images: Still not available directly from Sorftime\n- 1688 supplier images: Available from `ali1688_similar_product`\n\nThe workflow could be:\n1. Get Tiktok product details from Sorftime (ProductId, title, price, sales)\n2. Use the title to search 1688 via `ali1688_similar_product` \n3. Get the 1688 product image (which shows the actual product) and 1688 URL\n4. Store both the TK product info AND the 1688 supplier image/URL in Feishu\n\nThis is actually a workable solution! The 1688 image might actually be better than Tiktok product images in some cases because:\n- It shows the actual product without Tiktok shop overlays\n- It shows what customers will actually receive\n\n\n- It provides supply chain visibility and can be used for image-based product matching\n\nSo the 1688 image serves as a practical visual proxy for the TikTok product itself.\n","thinkingSignature":"105cadd736e639a975ec1ed6acad6dbdd669cc7449981bf7ba8cbbb457c7487a"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n这个接口有用！而且很关键——**它返回主图 URL！**\n\n```json\n{\n  \"标题\": \"空气炸锅批发...\",\n  \"主图\": \"https://cbu01.alicdn.com/img/ibank/...jpg\",  // ← 有图片！\n  \"URL\": \"https://detail.1688.com/offer/...html\",\n  \"价格\": 2.60,\n  \"卖家\": \"深圳市云智牛科技有限公司\"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 实际可用的工作流\n\n即使 TK 图片拿不到，我们可以这样组合：\n\n```\nTK产品详情（ Sorftime）\n    ↓ 标题\nali1688_similar_product 搜同款（ Sorftime）\n    ↓ 拿到1688主图 + 链接 + 价格\n写入飞书表格\n```\n\n**飞书表格里存的是：**\n- TK 产品标题 + 价格 + 销量\n- **1688 供应商主图**（有图片了！）\n- 1688 链接 + 拿货价\n- 计算出利润率和预估利润\n\n1688 图片虽然不是 TK 商品图，但**展示的是真实产品实物**，反而对选品更有参考价值——能看到产品实际长什么样。\n\n---\n\n## 关于 Sorftime CLI\n\nSorftime 如果出了 CLI，确实会更稳——直接命令行调用，不用走 MCP 中间层。但 MCP 已经够用了，关键还是 Key 要续上。\n\n**现在最现实的选择是：充值 Sorftime → 把 TK 数据 + 1688 图片组合进表格 → 先跑起来再说。**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":37079,"output":742,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37821,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778745696667,"responseId":"0654b46253e246724d0ea17ad286dc36"}}
